  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>고객의 시간</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-64568cde-270d-4ef1-9e43-45b9a6f40e2b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>이 가장 소중한</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-76d8b3e7-4179-421c-a773-6569f61d402f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e54c37e-94ad-428f-9078-c2ca41044e1b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-586bb70f-9147-480e-a789-aa25582e9bb3\" style=\"\">결론부터</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7a927ec1-5d2a-4624-ba1c-cd98527e5114\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5abcce6-2e6f-4970-a2bb-c4f2cd48cdfa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fea03846-d3e4-4a17-a38b-3354c6e17fdb\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>졸업작품은 급합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb0d50ce-0f63-4dfe-bed4-e7b921f927d2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bd64c452-381e-4637-b5d3-b45febcd4253\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0fe37fff-0f34-4387-a245-feba9da6b532\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1cb3d88d-ad96-4fcf-a1d0-f959ff5f74c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">경험상 졸업작품은 항상 납기가 생명인 경우가 많습니다. 제출용이든 행사용 포스터이든 통상적으로 보면 가장 중요한 것은 빠른 납기였습니다. 물론 학생이다 보니 가격도 합리적이어야 하고 퀄리티도 보장되어야 하지만 무엇보다 납기를 맞춰 줄 수 있느냐?에 대한 문의가 가장 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d33d333c-d378-466b-b03b-c19ff0bf1a04\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:459px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ced05f37-3570-4372-98ab-5a2b566d3cb9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-88cee060-c2ab-4fcb-919a-b9e6f8c4029d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a5decaf1-996f-468f-b062-a73eab7ff59d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">졸업작품용으로 제작하는 인쇄물은 어떤 것이든 제일 먼저 질문이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b8b6dd09-0821-4fef-96b2-bd47294b4d12\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-justify se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n<a class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42935305-9ca1-4a46-9d01-bfefe9d01c03\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-fdce23f8-caac-4328-a2ea-cbfa3a6a9943\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-770c7ec1-f8fe-4a95-b459-bf21b244f810\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>\"이날 납품이 가능할까요? ㅠ.ㅠ\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-79090ac3-f323-485a-8ed6-f3d2c3ae5b8a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-54ccf8e5-dc6b-4246-b899-3d6e99a09444\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c3d9eaac-4289-4788-9a85-f13bfa6e72d0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-974fadfb-fa4a-4e58-9f9e-1132ecdab4a6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 고객의 입장에서 가장 정확하고 확실한 답변을 드리고 있습니다. 할 수 있는데 없다고 해서 가격을 부풀리거나 할 수 없는데 할 수 있다고 해서 거래를 위해 고객의 시간을 빼앗는 경우는 절대 없습니다. 정확한 가부의 납기 유무를 가장 빠른 소통으로 알려드리고 있습니다. 이점은 (주)파파스컴퍼니 블로그를 걸고 분명히 말씀드립니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7b10a26a-de21-495c-884c-6a1e6ea6808c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-927b6564-b071-4a21-8ef8-c488b7ed7588\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00b2245c-fd61-4592-ba16-efc68779f12b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25891fbb-d70e-4747-b681-8589787deb08\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6858a7a4-7eb1-440a-87e7-c907e871502c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-743e5b4b-636c-4798-bd7f-dec3ef84da9b\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>졸업작품은 데이터가</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3289e8c7-ba32-4117-801f-812508c42d68\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f4665911-300a-4fa5-b575-31ca55db7573\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>깔끔하지 않습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-60e2dad7-9557-43e8-9995-a84b483e69fc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1872c827-94d3-426e-9d79-dfac1a94af39\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-98199fb3-0686-4137-acc6-ebdfeb7f39d6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-77042051-0260-450e-964f-76d27c32256d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대학생분들은 보통 디자인 초년생으로 인쇄 경험이 거의 없습니다. 실제 일러스트나 포토샵의 디자인이 인쇄로 처리되어 나오면 디자인 파일과의 다름에 놀라시는 분들도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e2f97f2b-cb58-4a65-9b99-d880ceab569c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-000a38d5-8677-46cb-bbd3-4e182bab2bcd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0d5d15e1-396d-4819-a876-b90cc030c677\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c8fd0d62-a649-4116-aa10-a42581a24b30\" style=\"color:#555555;\">예를 들어 색상이 화면하고 다르다든지 사이즈가 이상하게 오차가 발생했다고 한다든지 아니면 후공정을 전혀 모르시고 주문하시는 분들도 많이 있으십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-18300f97-49a3-48ea-be87-3aad97537fe9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-302d991e-ae7b-4102-bbf5-8e6bf43d7c45\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8670f3e1-c737-4aa4-882c-77831a961394\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2830f160-befa-40f9-9068-0dc84777813b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그러므로 항상 주문 전에 저희와의 거래와는 상관없이 업체와 소통을 꾸준히 하시기 바랍니다. 모르는 것 무조건 업체에 물어 보고 발주하시기 바랍니다. 물론 업체가 일일이 답변을 안 해주는 경우도 많습니다. 그렇더라도 집요(?) 하게 질문하시고 요구하시기 바랍니다, 그래야 사고가 나지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cbf37f77-2593-4829-b37f-e3ea8f13a491\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d53bb82a-9d32-4173-a411-5f5a358f65b9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-49ed894a-7bec-4086-8886-c137ed911a8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d468292b-5208-4a58-8343-2a6153d4abc3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주요 벨리데이션 체크사항은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-53063f70-48c3-472f-9658-08735ce083bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a6052f9b-15ed-4dbd-b5ea-48065a0f7a07\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">인쇄 색감</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b94e9440-03de-48d3-a70c-516bdc9639e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3107748c-5cc6-4126-8858-847499a73eb2\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">사이즈 여백</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a0cd3b33-d872-45ea-aa31-b9bf59f19bf9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4b7eb495-544b-4544-a5f6-99368cb9904d\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">후공정 상황</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0875982b-42ee-420e-8601-927bbbf228a1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-edc97d46-5efb-42b7-bc28-b4f621b61d45\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f8a0cb19-aaf1-423d-99ad-696be9759e9f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-da3dfee9-9ec1-4562-b8a0-ede802eb5c05\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2cdd6567-7b62-4687-b1cb-c8fa7228dcbc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-35e183c1-31d8-4d08-ba41-d0c13be761ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 부분은 추후에 자세하게 한번 다루겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-adfeffbf-e20b-4e11-af21-df672ceb55d7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-26760490-808f-4970-8f02-03a767c721b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-303b0f5d-9923-460f-a440-14fb86fbbaa6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b5a6e69f-a210-434c-b36f-ec359b9d9852\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>졸업작품은 소통이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7bc73ad4-cb0f-4595-94b2-57c66d098b52\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0ddb2207-c4b4-49e1-ba93-37ab56d2ab7b\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>가장 중요합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95e4b6b0-6ebf-4a2a-b146-da1f6c797409\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b4adc8b1-e49f-4539-a0de-bbfcda0c52e9\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b78a0252-3ade-4b91-82f5-f480fdfc3697\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-241bd433-b371-4710-9f97-b6d7f134203f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">납기와 디자인 미숙의 관점에서 가장 필요한 것은 인쇄 업체와 고객 간의 소통입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-67c63a7e-5de1-4360-89ac-07fe33e978d0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9a13a7a6-7a33-4972-9ed6-4e8399a323d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-646fe749-144e-44ae-8cb7-a173162fd0d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bc83f42d-8d00-44c5-b158-ff9e38492606\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반드시 물어 보고 확답을 받으신 후에 발주하시고 견적도 꼼꼼히 비교하시기 바랍니다. 무리하게 간보기 하라는 것은 아니지만 믿을 만한 업체인지를 파악하는 것은 매우 중합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a77156ab-0bba-465b-a9b4-e328dd323107\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-justify se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n<a class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f5b73184-936c-44e2-a46a-fcbf79f8d43e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e8da1d95-79fe-4a69-b281-f1283189807c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b41cb643-5131-4c8c-8be5-ff41e109ef9f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#9bdfff;\">가장 신뢰 있는 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하십시오. 이것이 정답입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-645c6b01-0dbd-4f8e-b63a-42ab5b99751f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-justify se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n<a class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-66d7b6ab-3b47-4d8d-acee-8f922460a606\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3483d9dc-9093-4c0d-8014-763b69f11798\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81191235-d4ae-4ceb-b212-c85f988e11d3\" style=\"\">디자인에 대한 모자이크 요청이 있어 모자이크 처리했습니다.</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-31cddd1f-55e0-4823-b7c5-2c1326e6dcb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20600189-3dd5-4840-ab87-48eef7801c98\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-47f9258b-4d96-416c-9ff5-6ddfce450923\" style=\"\">작업 일지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-327ed733-a11e-4cc1-84dc-c5a037087163\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:641px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-569a63b4-c19b-4e36-8170-db122e29916b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7f3954e9-77d1-49b2-91be-bba5fe4edc3e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99e893dc-6bb2-424c-9cb2-b3a4a4afcfd6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">토요일 오후 네이버 톡톡을 통해 문의가 와서 카톡으로 소통했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2f1e69da-4b1d-4551-81d5-f3b1d62b96d2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d55852a1-9807-41b7-91ff-2f58a6b21f6d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">동아예술대에 다니시는 학생으로 급한 졸업작품용 포스터 제작 문의였습니다. 데이터는 작업이 되어 있고 월요일 당일에 퀵으로 발송 요청을 하셨습니다. 토요일 문의를 받은 거라 생산 상황을 알지 못했지만 일단은 고객님의 급하신 상황을 인지했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c9138e36-ff3e-4f36-9f80-eee3b6346248\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1a5cb1e-7140-430a-9e35-d789a9c7161a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b9a035cd-a149-4220-b243-5243332388e1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bcbc03c3-a9a1-4242-9250-a76a81fc8c31\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8587be3c-19cc-4b20-b84b-49f093fb3bee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-403d421d-71b2-4ea8-89bc-ed456e23e023\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>졸업작품은 항상 급합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8fe30d5c-00f5-4fd1-961c-1d5f190e6e44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-315d3ced-3b79-444f-a35b-83ec558eece6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d25f9e5e-5085-44e6-adfd-d5abe5e5eafd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6b9a6d8c-6e1b-4328-86d6-bf1909591261\" style=\"color:#555555;\">저희 경험상 졸업작품이나 대학교 행사용 인쇄물은 항상 급한 경우가 대부분이었습니다. 이 문의도 토요일이었음에도 불구하고 월요일 오후까지 납품이 가능할지에 대한 문의였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-76d016ad-b370-48f2-bc84-5ca5da09d248\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-40610c45-931a-4d52-ab51-43dd5f562609\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-940cbc20-9e9b-4489-95d6-c3fbc123defa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b1b9433-c9b9-47ce-9143-1bf0c586a60f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수량은 장소 곳곳에 붙이는 포스터로 60장이었습니다. 별다른 후공정이 없는 일반 재단이었지만 수량도 60장이고 데이터도 월요일 전송 예정이어서 납기에 부담이 있는 포스터 인쇄물이었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1e81cd1c-aed8-4760-bb3a-c4367d21070a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:640px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-16313234-08b7-4110-bd72-acd85ae41d95\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ed5c1ad8-0b16-4330-acf2-645885b3506d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-93b7e6e3-ca30-491e-8f8e-c0924abfb1bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">더군다나 충무로에서 퀵을 출발시켜 퀵비를 절감하고 싶어 하셔서 더더욱 생산 일정에 대한 고민이 있었습니다. 하지만 100장 미만의 소량이고 데이터만 깔끔하다면 가능해 보여 진행을 결정하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-71783fde-1fa8-4549-b311-33b62cd2de96\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-788e1ded-4109-4772-ad43-accbc876c796\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-781cad03-1d2c-4bad-ae85-3e0065ffffda\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-35a23dd7-4526-46d1-b144-e1e9f9f563ee\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">급한 대로 생산시설을 준비시키고 항상 납기는 할 수 있다 없다를 정확하게 말씀드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a5085785-7a00-4ac9-bcf3-e970629e76e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-571eadcf-7965-4321-9c9c-6e2c0be59a91\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1e950d0e-0fb8-4585-9a8e-a90746aa3317\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2fd7a5d2-3521-4d75-a48c-da92e1746996\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2643d3f0-8014-41d8-b618-2d503db6faf7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5d6186d1-ac6f-4303-b4ba-508f66a7e113\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>졸업작품은 항상 데이터가 깔끔하지 않습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-de97bf3e-c55c-4fa5-a591-053b35c43bff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b12a7e7c-565d-4ab8-bba1-07abd834afb9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-df68218c-be21-42d9-a156-0d2bd5cb09e7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-83055d2b-dcbb-480c-b45b-e47f78b5bed1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">졸업작품은 대학생이 디자인을 하다 보니 데이터가 전문가에 비해 완벽하지 않은 경우를 종종 봅니다. 물론 완벽하게 디자인하여 제공하시는 분도 많지만 거의 인쇄 초년생으로 디자인이 깔끔하지 않고 또한 데이터 용량도 큰 경우를 많이 봤습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b04712c1-6829-401a-b881-bfaee2cd7408\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:643px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e2faab23-f672-45da-95ab-0fc6367374ca\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-542912dd-f9f5-4b71-b62c-855140bcda44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d6e47dd5-e175-4b2b-a6f7-b0fc734b83ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">역시 데이터에 이미지 링크가 빠져있어 X로 처리된 이미지가 보였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cf4bd644-8cac-477a-b5a4-2a0555301fca\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:306px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d0b06d7f-2ad9-452a-ad0b-b962f9ee2019\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3cdce587-1f08-4070-a047-22bc862b3f8f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6e3e4a97-97eb-406e-ac76-3d2466010b3b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 항상 고객의 데이터를 검증하는 작업을 합니다. 이 적합성 검사를 통과해야 인쇄 작업을 진행합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-68ba3ba0-02cd-47fd-85fa-e18fa4f4d3a0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:635px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb571d66-73b8-4ec5-8e92-b0bc415f646c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0315630e-ef61-4b1b-af6a-9236f89b4cc7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-59382197-0f42-4d09-b2d3-6a78ec87a757\" style=\"color:#555555;\">저희 디자인팀장님과 데이터 작업자와의 소통을 연결시켰습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ddb30322-4376-40e4-8acc-e5293bf5f1f3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-96e92fb8-b049-4d8d-9cfa-70ce16de57e2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0a768895-9b40-4604-9f97-27337bbb0350\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a33a1ee0-1d91-487c-b7e5-b6b065e29c1e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4d087b5b-7005-4060-ba14-5323da9f0edf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cd01ec78-5f1c-44e0-b25b-d2dd1db9c603\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>고객과의 소통이 가장 중요합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e8d89b57-b194-454d-b63e-e53323f2cc96\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d09ad485-9981-4590-9aeb-73b199917d8e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-45d1069d-ab45-4b01-922a-eb2b7020446d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-517f8545-24e5-44b9-8d03-08bf24406f02\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아무리 작은 주문, 아무리 적은 금액의 인쇄물이라도 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 고객과의 소통이 가장 중요하게 생각합니다. 항상 고객과의 카톡을 연결하고 전화나 메일, 또는 카카오 톡으로 소통하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-44f23f08-5cea-4fd4-8faf-960cfe8aa6e7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4cce4b56-e75f-48a3-b4c2-78754f2c4c53\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bf539b91-b6b8-49cd-95b7-18acab528720\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bb242fb8-d8a1-4ea8-ba90-03d90e3e4d7a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">인쇄는 확인, 확인, 그리고 또 확인이 가장 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ffb9ab6c-e5cb-4238-bb0b-60d278a4b24e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:641px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223885003727/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4b8d446-5ec4-4295-b1a3-7ba6c6a725d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-abf47b79-253a-4436-93d6-a1bfb4dd4672\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-771e9f11-c38c-42f2-b707-bbf696275573\" style=\"color:#555555;\">토요일 오후에 주문의뢰를 하시고 월요일 11시에 작업 완료하고 3시에 퀵을 출발시켰습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-082d78fd-e142-4a42-9746-92f453902da2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-794e45cd-33ad-4ed6-a580-39abf56c970e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-53638608-2271-469d-8f00-c9e548fb57b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bfb26025-560b-40e8-ad20-8a815188d54d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정확한 납기로 항상 고객의 믿음에 부합되도록 노력하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d2eaf8c0-019e-4d6c-ae59-345512a43a6d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-76fe54fe-9c2b-427d-9555-b51080079b7d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c5002042-b9e8-4a8a-befa-9d31a92efffe\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-567b73d6-05ba-4d71-b21e-897cfe500349\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>고객님께 드리는 약속</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1046fb71-93d9-478b-b9a6-108a010f3ec1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06df70d1-a4fb-4461-b6d7-fef143852cdf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주말 언제 어디서든 카톡 연결이나 톡톡 가능합니다. 항상 문의를 먼저 하시고 발주하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bc19051a-1a8a-4115-87ba-dca847c81d85\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4030578d-8e57-466a-b1d4-3afe37e94a67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223885003727#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}